data.description: Incredible East Medford Home & Location! Peaceful, quiet cul-de-sac. Sellers have recently remodeled the master shower & it's gorgeous with tile surround, new flooring,  & new fixtures. Also, newer heating & air conditioning system, some newer backyard fencing, newer water heater, and a well-maintained 8-year-old roof. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan, featuring both a large living room & den (could be used as a 4th bedroom or office). Vaulted ceilings, ceiling fans, and large windows allow the home to be light & bright. Nice sized kitchen w/custom cabinets, hardwood flooring, pantry, granite countertops, & stainless-steel appliances. Large master suite with a private slider to the huge, beautiful back yard w/times sprinkler/drip system, an in-ground fire pit, & vibrant flower beds. Oversized garage, RV parking, and only 1 block to the Dog-Friendly Kennedy Park, N Medford High School, & scenic walking paths. Bring your clients, they will love it.
